Come in. I've got some pork chops.

523
01:23:58,200 --> 01:24:00,000
‎当然啦 你从来都不跟我说
Of course, you never call ahead.

524
01:24:00,080 --> 01:24:04,880
‎你可以打个电话 说你要回来的
You could have told me you were coming.

525
01:24:04,960 --> 01:24:06,760
‎我可以提前准备好
I would have prepared.

526
01:24:06,840 --> 01:24:10,280
‎从来都是逼我临场发挥
I always have to think on my feet.

527
01:24:34,000 --> 01:24:36,760
‎亲爱的 能告诉我们出什么事了吗 
Honey, what's going on?

528
01:24:36,840 --> 01:24:40,920
‎什么意思 什么事都没有 ‎我就是来看望一下我的父母
What do you mean? Nothing's going on. I'm just here to visit you.

529
01:24:41,840 --> 01:24:44,480
‎你妈妈认为 人们只有在遭遇危机时
Your mom is convinced that people buy motorcycles

530
01:24:44,560 --> 01:24:47,760
‎才会去买摩托车
when they're going through some kind of crisis.

531
01:24:50,080 --> 01:24:52,720
‎亲爱的 你就快30岁了
Honey, you'll be 30 soon.

532
01:24:53,400 --> 01:24:56,960
‎如果一切无恙 ‎你应该跟老公一起庆祝你的生日
If you were okay, you'd be spending your birthday with your husband,

533
01:24:57,040 --> 01:24:59,800
‎庆祝你们的初遇
celebrating the anniversary of your first meeting.

534
01:24:59,880 --> 01:25:02,480
‎-而据我所知… ‎-我陷入爱河了 妈妈
-As far as I know-- -I'm in love with someone else.

535
01:25:13,560 --> 01:25:14,640
‎他叫纳乔
His name is Nacho.

536
01:25:17,320 --> 01:25:18,920
‎亲爱的 给我拿支烟
Honey, get me a cigarette.

537
01:25:20,120 --> 01:25:23,560
‎但我们说好了的 以后不再抽烟了
But we agreed that we wouldn't smoke anymore.

538
01:25:23,640 --> 01:25:25,960
‎拜托 给我拿支烟 
Please, bring me a cigarette!

539
01:25:29,480 --> 01:25:30,320
‎那好吧
All right then.

540
01:26:20,120 --> 01:26:25,040
‎告诉我 亲爱的 如果你不是 ‎马西莫的老婆 你会选谁 
Honey, if you weren't married to Massimo, who would you choose?

541
01:26:27,920 --> 01:26:29,880
‎问题就是我不知道
The problem is, I don't know.

542
01:26:30,840 --> 01:26:34,000
‎等你知道问题的答案以后 ‎你就知道该怎么做了
When you have the answer, you'll know what to do.

543
01:26:38,200 --> 01:26:39,040
‎是啊…
All right…

544
01:26:56,520 --> 01:26:58,280
‎跟你说一个小秘密
I'll tell you a little secret.

545
01:26:58,920 --> 01:27:03,360
‎我觉得就是这个秘密 ‎让我的婚姻坚持了35年的
I think it's what's kept our marriage alive for 35 years.

