01:27:05,640 --> 01:27:11,080
‎记住 在一段关系中 女人一定要自私
Remember, a woman must be selfish in a relationship.

547
01:27:12,800 --> 01:27:14,960
‎如果你把自己的幸福放在第一位
If you put your own happiness first,

548
01:27:15,040 --> 01:27:18,080
‎你就会不惜一切代价 ‎让幸福能够得以延续 对吧 
you'll do whatever it takes to make it last, right?

549
01:27:18,840 --> 01:27:20,840
‎你也会珍惜你们的关系
You will cherish your relationship.

550
01:27:22,520 --> 01:27:25,440
‎但那必须得是一段不会摧毁你的关系
But it can't be a relationship that destroys you.

551
01:27:27,840 --> 01:27:32,160
‎记住 一个只为男人而活的女人
Remember that a woman who lives only for her man

552
01:27:33,680 --> 01:27:35,440
