But I was pissed off about not understanding, so I learned.

589
01:33:13,480 --> 01:33:17,080
‎也许我说得不够流利 ‎但我全都能听懂
Maybe I'm not a fluent speaker, but I understand everything.

590
01:33:17,160 --> 01:33:19,280
