‎操 我刚刚说了“干他丫的”
Fuck. I just said, "shoot."

596
01:33:33,760 --> 01:33:36,720
‎我宁愿他把自己干掉 而不是你或我
I'd rather him shoot himself than you or me.

597
01:33:36,800 --> 01:33:41,440
‎小奥 好了 他现在什么动作都没有 ‎这一定是有原因的 对吧 
Olo, stop. There must be a reason he hasn't done anything about it yet.

598
01:33:41,520 --> 01:33:46,680
‎你到底有没有听我说话  ‎马西莫是不会原谅不忠的行为的
Are you even listening to me? Massimo won't forgive cheating.

599
01:33:46,760 --> 01:33:47,840
‎听着
-Listen. -Shit.

600
01:33:48,440 --> 01:33:51,920
‎我并不惧怕自己的丈夫 ‎我不会躲着他
I'm not scared of my own husband. I won't hide from him.

601
01:33:54,040 --> 01:33:55,000
‎我这就回去
I'm coming back.

602
01:33:56,160 --> 01:34:02,120
‎随你怎么做吧 我在研究…撤离计划
Do what you want. I'm working on… an escape plan.

603
01:34:03,200 --> 01:34:05,280
‎小奥 放轻松 抽根烟 好吗 
Olo, relax. Have a cigarette, okay?

604
01:34:05,360 --> 01:34:08,840
‎你他妈以为我现在在做什么  ‎我一直都在抽烟 
What the hell do you think I'm doing? I can't stop smoking!

605
01:34:10,520 --> 01:34:11,400
‎好吧 再见…
Okay, bye.

606
01:34:24,240 --> 01:34:26,200
‎爸爸 我得回西西里了
Dad, I have to go back to Sicily.

607
01:34:26,880 --> 01:34:27,720
‎好的
Okay.

608
01:34:29,720 --> 01:34:33,240
‎但我们先回座位去吧 ‎因为我点了一个苹果派
But first, let's go back to the table. I ordered some apple pie.

609
01:34:34,080 --> 01:34:35,240
‎走吧
Come on.

610
01:35:09,440 --> 01:35:10,440
‎您要去哪里

611
01:35:10,520 --> 01:35:11,480
‎有劳说英语
English, please.

612
01:35:25,360 --> 01:35:26,680
‎法比奥罗西先生
Mr. Fabio Rossi,

613
01:35:28,040 --> 01:35:31,480
‎我跟你说别逼我时 ‎你是哪里没听懂吗 
what did you not understand when I told you not to push me?

614
01:35:36,840 --> 01:35:37,720
‎劳拉…
Laura…

615
01:35:39,400 --> 01:35:44,080
‎我来到这里 ‎不惜搭上性命以及我父亲的生意
by coming here, I'm risking my life and also my father's life in business.

616
01:35:44,680 --> 01:35:47,920
‎我们和马西莫约定好了 ‎永不进入他的地盘
We have a pact with Massimo not to enter his territory.

617
01:35:48,720 --> 01:35:49,960
‎但你知道吗 
And you know what?

618
01:35:50,800 --> 01:35:52,000
‎我根本不在乎…
I didn't give a fuck…

619
01:35:53,800 --> 01:35:55,200
‎因为我需要见你
because I needed to see you.

620
01:35:59,320 --> 01:36:00,160
‎小蜜蜂…
Bee…

621
01:36:02,840 --> 01:36:03,680
‎拜托
Please.

622
01:36:06,160 --> 01:36:09,080
‎听我说完 然后随你怎么做
Hear me out, and then do what you want.

623
01:36:10,280 --> 01:36:11,360
‎就像一直以来那样
As you always do.

624
01:36:18,880 --> 01:36:21,560
‎好吧 法比奥罗西先生 我们走吧
Okay, Mr. Fabio Rossi. Let's go.

625
01:36:23,080 --> 01:36:26,600
‎你知道地址的 你以前在那里当花匠
You know the address. You used to work there as a gardener.

626
01:36:44,960 --> 01:36:46,920
‎那件事我已经道过歉了
I've already apologized for that.

627
